OL,3,CVennells: Claims post office had
OL,4,C'driven subpostmaster to suicide...
OL,5,Cunhelpful'
OL,7,FAccusations from Alan Bates the Post
OL,8,FOffice was to blame after a
OL,9,Fsubpostmaster deliberately stepped in
OL,10,Ffront of a bus were "unhelpful", said
OL,11,Fformer boss Paula Vennells at the Post
OL,12,FOffice inquiry.
OL,14,FMartin Griffiths walked in front of a
OL,15,Fbus on 23 September 2013, after he had
OL,16,Fbeen deemed culpable for an armed
OL,17,Frobbery at his Hope Farm Post Office
OL,18,Fbranch in in May 2013.
