OL,5,Cunhelpful'
OL,7,FHe had also previously written to the
OL,8,FPost Office in July 2013 about a
OL,9,F#39,000 shortfall at his branch
OL,10,Fbetween February 2012 and May 2013.
OL,12,FHe was sacked in July of the same year.
OL,14,FAppearing at the Horizon IT inquiry
OL,15,Ffor the first time, former CEO Paula
OL,16,FVennells said accusations that the
OL,17,FPost Office was to blame were
OL,18,F"unhelpful... at that stage."
