OL,7,FMr Griffiths died in hospital three
OL,8,Fweeks later.
OL,10,FAn email chain between former Post
OL,11,FOffice general counsel Susan Crichton
OL,12,Fand Ms Vennells was also shown.
OL,14,FIn the email Ms Vennells says "if it
OL,15,Fis an attempted suicide, as we sadly
OL,16,Fknow, there are usually several
OL,17,Fcontributory factors".
