OL,7,FAsked why she was raising the fact
OL,8,Fthat there were usually several
OL,9,Fcontributory factors, she said she was
OL,10,F"very sorry".
OL,12,FShe added: "Every email you will see
OL,13,Ffrom me about Mr Griffiths, I start
OL,14,Fwith him and how he was and how his
OL,15,Ffamily are. The Post Office took far
OL,16,Ftoo long to deal with it."
