OL,7,FShe added that as Chief Executive, she
OL,8,Fhad to communicate "something so
OL,9,Fserious as this to the board" and was
OL,10,Ftrying to find out "whether there was
OL,11,Fanything else behind it".
OL,13,FShe then broke down in tears as she
OL,14,Fmentioned a previous experience of a
OL,15,FPost Office colleague taking their own
OL,16,Flife and spoke to their family who
OL,17,Fexplained that there were "other
OL,18,Fissues involved".
