OL,7,FSpeaking of Mr Griffiths's case, she
OL,8,Fsaid: "I imagine that what I was doing
OL,9,Fhere in this email was recalling that
OL,10,Fprevious incident, but what you will
OL,11,Fsee is that in every email I wrote on
OL,12,Fthis, my first concern was for Mr
OL,13,FGriffiths and his family, and as I
OL,14,Fsaid in my statement, sorry is an
OL,15,Finadequate word, I'm just so sorry
OL,16,Fthat Mr Griffiths isn't here today."
